### 3.1. Club Mapping & State Parameters

Selecting a club sets the initial velocity vector magnitude (via the Smash Factor ratio) and establishes the initial backspin angular velocity ($\omega_0$):

| Club Type  | Launch Angle ($\theta_0$) | Initial Backspin ($\omega_0$) | Smash Factor ($S_f$) |
| :--------- | :------------------------ | :---------------------------- | :------------------- |
| **Driver** | $12^\circ$                | 2,500 RPM                     | 1.48                 |
